divs: Sighting DetailsWe were taking pictures of a corn crop for the university located in our area of Louisiana. I did not notice this "disc" while taking the picture. We were in a rural area so noise wasn't an issue, but we heard nothing and saw nothing until I downloaded this picture to my computer. I took two consecutive pictures with a Nikon D60 and the "disc" was only in one of the two pictures. In the second picture, it is gone.
